name: Cyberpunk Cityscape #23
description: A futuristic cyberpunk cityscape rendered in deep purple and blue tones, featuring illuminated skyscrapers with neon pink and blue outlines against a star-filled night sky. The urban skyline is punctuated by glowing teal and purple windows across various buildings, while a luminous yellow moon hovers in the upper right, completing this atmospheric nocturnal metropolis scene.
